    <h1>{{scenario.label}}</h1>

    <h2>FIRE Results</h2>

    <p>You will be FIRE in <strong>{{yearsToFi}}</strong> years.<p>
    <p>You will be FIRE in <strong>{{yearOfFi}}</strong>.</p>

    <h2>Your details</h2>
    <ul>
        <li> Age: {{scenario.age}}</li>
        <li> Income: ${{scenario.income}}</li>
        <li> Annual expenses: ${{scenario.outgoings}}</li>
        <li> Net worth: ${{scenario.investmentAmount}}</li>
        <li> Return rate: {{scenario.returnRate}}%</li>
        <li> Current super balance: ${{scenario.super}}</li>
        <li> Employer super guarantee: {{scenario.superGuarantee}}%</li>
        <li> Inflation rate {{scenario.inflationRate}}%</li>
    </ul>


    <h2>Pre Super </h2>


    <ul>
        <li> Super preservation age: {{superPreservationAge}}</li>
        <li> Years until you reach preservation: {{yearsUntilPreservation}}</li>
        <li> Year of preservation {{preservationYear}}</li>
