        <li> Monthly expenduture: ${{ monthlyExpenses}}</li>
        <li> Networth needed in order to sustain current lifestyle until preservation age right now: ${{currentPv}}</li>
        <li>Networth needed in order to sustain current lifestyle until preservation age after you hit your Pre Super Number: ${{postPv}}</li>
