        <li>How much Super you will have at the end of reaching your Pre Super Number: {{superResult}}</li>
        <li>How much you need to have in Super at the start of FIRE for it to grow to you FI number: ${{superRequiredForFi}}</li>
        <li>How much more $ you need to put in before you FIRE {{superNeeded}} </li>
        <li>How long in years will it take you to get to your number factoring in your current net worth, inlfation rate and rate of return: {{yearsToSuperTarget}}</li>
